document_data.name: Siela
document_data.mainbody: '''Siela''' was a female [[elf]] who resided in the [[Malar's Throat]] district of [[Port Nyanzaru]], [[Chult]] in the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].{{Cite adventurers league/A City on the Edge|25}}
document_data.History: During the events of the [[death curse]] in the late 15{{th}} century DR, Siela was one of several citizens of Malar's Throat to be captured by a group of [[pterafolk]] who attacked the district. She realized that she was to be sacrificed to the jungle, and was placed as an offering in a cluster of thorny brambles alongside a [[tabaxi]] named [[Ashen Rock]]. Despite her frantic calls for help, she was dragged screaming into the brambles and killed by [[Twig blight|twig]] and [[needle blight]]s.
